A good work awaits you
We had planned with 3 colleagues to take 10g of speed, 1g of MDMA and 2 vials of LSD,
Have a good Friday evening everyone
We consumed 5 grams of speed plus all the drugs,
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I go to work just from 9am to 12pm in the afternoon,
We have not continued,
I continue to shoot darts on my side and shoot fast.
In the afternoon's end, the evening arrives with two more colleagues joining us. We had decided to take LSD on the beach (Personally, I wasn't reassured).
A colleague handed me the glass with a drop from the LSD vial.
I hesitated at first, then I told myself, "Go ahead," I took it (something I shouldn't have).
The evening continues normally and the two other so-called colleagues decided to make us work overtime excessively...
On that famous beach there were people and one of the two colleagues said, "There's no one looking for shit, we're going to beat them up ..."
I tell myself the product should go down because I couldn't fight like him
so eventually I forced myself to resist the product,
