Impossible to sleep, I'm thinking and at the slightest noise I go out with a bat...
The day rises and I start to fall asleep because I have just realized that there is nothing,
The night passes normally.
I get up and I am still under the effect of LSD and the rest
I tell myself it's normal
So we were Sunday and the next day I had to work.
The day passes normally.
I tap a bolt then I tighten it.
The Sunday passed and Monday arrives
I still feel like I need to shave.
I still tell myself these normal things with the box that I took...
So at 2 PM, I had to go to work
I eat a little and I leave a big speed trace to get the fish at the end...
So I take the car and I go to the party
arrive at the bar, as soon as I open the store I start to feel dizzy, my heart starts beating at 200 and I feel like I'm going to faint,
